query:
SELECT userId, endpoint, method, statusCode, duration, timestamp 
FROM auditLogs 
WHERE timestamp > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 5 MINUTE) 
ORDER BY timestamp DESC 
LIMIT 20;
